text.tspan: It takes a village to build an operating system.

flowRoot.flowPara: Champions of Justice. Defenders of Peace. This team of dedicated moderators exists to protect and serve.
One team to rule them all.
One team to bring them all,
and in the darkness, bind them.
Fast paced, interconnected, ahead of the curve, and pushing you to the edge of your seat.
Sleep is for the weak. They eat in terms of megabytes, speak in algorithms, and bleed binary.
They live amongst the clouds, weaving endless webs of cross-browser compatability. What you dream, they create.
Call them obsessive compulsive, detail-oriented, or just plain pixel pushers. Design isn't what they do, it's what they are.
